calls a peaceful nuclear device israel is thought to have 
produced and stockpiled nuclear weapons pakistan is thought to be 
very close to being able to build a bomb and there have been 
reports that brazil and argentina have conducted nuclear weapons 
research according to us government officials and leonard 
spector an expert on nuclear issues at the carnegie endowment for 
peace and author of several books on proliferation 
