roxbury incorporation project that got the secession movement 
started 
right now hardly any of the teachers send their kids to our 
schools he said most of the police live outside the 
community if the police live in the community then theyre 
protecting their home if they just work in the community then 
theyre protecting their job 
jones says his support of the proposal is to blame for an 
attempt to evict him from his apartment the owners of the building 
insist the matter has nothing to do with politics 
