the case involves gary eagan who was sentenced to 35 years in 
prison for attempted murder 
eagan telephoned chicago police on may 16 1982 and told them he 
found a dead naked woman along the shore of lake michigan in 
indiana 
when he led police there the woman was still alive and upon 
seeing eagan exclaimed why did you stab me 
she later testified she was was picked up by eagan and some 
