some of the protesters and was jokingly offered 5 for one of 
coffees hows this she said giving away one of the cups 
without breaking stride 
before returning to her assignment of helping usher arrestees 
onto a bus the officer slipped on a pair of plastic gloves and 
then hid them from view with a pair of white mittens 
