barbara cox anthony samuel joseph frankino johnnie bryan hunt 
jerry j moore and harry weinberg 
at least 40 other forbes 400 members finished high school only 
at least 296 attended college of whom 242 graduated fortysix 
hold mbas while 16 have law degrees 
