family remains interested in working with kroger to strengthen 
the company and enhance their restructuring by providing additional 
equity 
he declined to comment on whether the haft bid has been 
withdrawn but representatives of the haft family had contact 
with kroger management last week about remaining involved with the 
company a source said 
