id have preferred it if youd not called me privately 
pollack said angrily it isnt appropriate to call up a judge on 
a saturday afternoon 
the developments marked the angriest exchanges yet between 
pollack and the drexel legal team fighting the securities and 
exchange commissions wideranging civilfraud charges 
the sec charges filed last month after an intense 
investigation allege drexel its highyield bond chief michael 
